text: Osvald Rechke (born 27 September 1883, date of death unknown) was a Russian sports shooter. He competed in three events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1883 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Russian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Russia Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kyiv
